    • commandHelp

      @Contract(value="_, _ -> new", pure=true) @NotNull public static @NotNull Component commandHelp(@NotNull @NotNull String keyPrefix, boolean appendHelp)
      Creates a command help.

      This method creates a help message for the command by adding .command-line and .description to the prefix of the given key.

      The keys of the referenced messages are keyPrefix.command-line and keyPrefix.description.

      If appendHelp is true, the keys of the messages are keyPrefix.help.command-line and keyPrefix.help.description.

      Parameters:
      keyPrefix - the key prefix of the messages
      appendHelp - whether to append .help to the key prefix
      Returns:
      the created Component
